strong interest in political science and tougher legislation to 
help the disabled spurred her interest in law school 
ms prince said she is considering setting up practices in 
several legal areas public interest civil rights or contract law 
i have a very strong interest in education and education of 
the handicapped she said that comes from what ive seen in 
how hard it is to get an education 
