renewal in czechoslovakia these unjustified actions had longterm 
negative consequences history proved that it is extremely 
important even in the most complex international situations to 
use political means for the settling of any problem to strongly 
observe principles of sovereignty independence and 
noninterference in internal affairs in relations between states 
in line with the principles of the warsaw pact 
the soviet announcement likened the situation in 1968 to the 
current political upheaval in czechoslovakia where demonstrations 
