we dont ask opera singers to do wagner eight times a week 
and honestly i am exhausted she says portia is a very big 
quite tiring part 
the blonde bigboned actress is bestknown to american 
audiences for her portrayal of mirabehn mahatma gandhis acolyte 
in the oscarwinning movie about the indian leaders life and as 
