ago in the english midlands city of coventry 
then she recalls portia struck her as a bit of a knowall 
now she finds her a miraculous character and attributes her 
shift in perceptions to halls direction 
with shakespeare he is the master he can tell you how to do 
it james says if i was going to see shakespeare for the first 
time i would choose a peter hall production he may not go for 
innovation but he does the play 
hall says he admired jamess natural musicality and sense of 
rhythm shesa very intelligent feisty actress 
james says the director encouraged her to explore the 
contradictions of a character who can seem dismissive and even 
