statement was a progress report rather than a full earnings 
announcement 
britains beecham group plc and philadelphiabased smithkline 
beckman corp merged in july through an exchange of shares 
creating the worlds secondlargest pharmaceuticals company after 
rahway njbased merck and co smithkline beecham said its 
pretax profit for the nine months ended sept 30 came to 5873 
million pounds or the equivalent 920 million compared with 5243 
million pounds or 822 million in the same period a year ago 
